    <title>Hexo博客安装</title>
    <link href="https://blog.xiao2024.cn/posts/11a4/"/>
    <id>https://blog.xiao2024.cn/posts/11a4/</id>
    <published>2024-06-04T02:23:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-06-04T17:34:52.700Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/zhheo/Post-Abstract-AI@0.18/tianli_gpt.css"></p><script>let tianliGPT_postSelector = '#post #article-container';let tianliGPT_key = 'IeAj85qh38b';</script><script src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/zhheo/Post-Abstract-AI@0.18/tianli_gpt.min.js"></script><div class="tip info"><p>本篇为博客的安装记录 📝</p></div><h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>本博客使用 Github Pages + Hexo 进行搭建。</p><h1 id="入门"><a href="#入门" class="headerlink" title="入门"></a>入门</h1><p>首先，你得有一个Github账号</p><h1 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h1><h2 id="安装node-js"><a href="#安装node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装node.js"></a>安装node.js</h2><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>进入 node.js 官网：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager">Node.js 官网</a><br>按照自己的机器选择对应的版本下载</p>              </div>            </details><h2 id="安装Git"><a href="#安装Git" class="headerlink" title="安装Git"></a>安装Git</h2><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>进入 Git 官网：<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">Git 官网</a><br>Git 安装参考：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/jytx/p/5602927.html">Git 安装教程</a></p>              </div>            </details><h2 id="检查是否安装成功"><a href="#检查是否安装成功" class="headerlink" title="检查是否安装成功"></a>检查是否安装成功</h2><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>同时按下 Win + R 键打开运行窗口,输入 <code>cmd</code> ，然后输入以下命令，查看是否安装成功。<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git --version</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>              </div>            </details><h1 id="Hexo安装"><a href="#Hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装"></a>Hexo安装</h1><h2 id="创建文件"><a href="#创建文件" class="headerlink" title="创建文件"></a>创建文件</h2><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>选择位置新建文件夹（如D:\Hexo-Blog），进入该文件夹，右键在终端中打开，输入以下命令<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>              </div>            </details><h2 id="初始化Hexo"><a href="#初始化Hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化Hexo"></a>初始化Hexo</h2><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击 查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>输入第一条指令初始化Hexo，第二个命令安装 deployer 将 Hexo 部署到 Github Pages<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>Hexo 安装完成后，将会在指定文件夹中创建好所需要的文件</p>              </div>            </details><h1 id="本地部署"><a href="#本地部署" class="headerlink" title="本地部署"></a>本地部署</h1><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>输入指令<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>在浏览器中输入 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 查看效果</p>              </div>            </details><h1 id="部署到-Github"><a href="#部署到-Github" class="headerlink" title="部署到 Github"></a>部署到 Github</h1><details class="folding-tag" green><summary> 点击查看 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>到目前为止本地博客就成功搭建了，但是只能通过本地连接查看，要让其他人也能够访问我们的博客，就需要将博客部署到 Github Pages 上</p><div class="progress"><div class="progress-bar-animated progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-yellow"  style="width: 30%" aria-valuenow="30" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><p>未完待续</p></div></div>              </div>            </details>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
